title: The Prophecy Club - The Police State: Coming soon
description:
This DVD, by Stan Johnson, is updated every 12 to 18 months on the coming Police State with the latest information on the following:* Who is behind the World Government.* What the Globalists plans are, and * How those without the Mark will be found by using cell phones, surveillance cameras, Global ID, microchips, and public transportation. A totalitarian society created to find, log, idenify and track every person with the hidden agenda to force everyone to take the Mark of the Beast or lose their head. 2 hrs. 40 mins.
